	<li><a href="/en/government_in_ireland/european_government/eu_institutions/european_ombudsman.html">European Ombudsman</a><br>The European Ombudsman safeguards the fundamental rights of     citizens living in Europe by ensuring open and accountable administrations     within the European Union.</li>
	
